<h1 style="text-align: center;">User preferences</h1>
<ul>
<li>Introduction</li>
<ul>
<li>One patient record:</li>
<ul>
<li>The main goal of the project is to help the members of the
personal Care Team of the patient to share information about the
patient, i.e. to access the patient record.&nbsp; In order to share
patient information in an efficient way, there is in principle only one
common patient record. </li>
</ul>
<li>Different views:</li>
<ul>
<li>Since the Care Team is multidisciplinary, the users look at
this common patient record in different ways, depending on their roles
and professional background.&nbsp; Therefore it is important that the
users can mamnage their own preferences.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<li>Remark:</li>
<ul>
<li>The project is based here on a "patient centric record" and
no more to make completely different softwares for every professional
group, as GP, specialists, nurses, paramedical professionals, ...&nbsp;
The problem was that&nbsp; separate software had very difficult to
share information. </li>
</ul>
</ul>
