</ul>
<li>Role in the organization, affiliations:</li>
<ul>
<li> <br />
</li>
</ul>
<li>Delegated permissions:</li>
<ul>
<li>Which computer tasks in hte system. </li>
</ul>
<li>Contacts:</li>
<ul>
<li>Addres, telephones, Email, .... </li>
</ul>
<li>User preferences:</li>
<ul>
<li>Language:</li>
<li>Types of views:</li>
<ul>
<li>In general in function of professional profile:</li>
<ul>
<li>Information relevant to the role of the user and taking
account of the permissions. </li>
<li>Default options will be proposed but may be modified
according to personal preferences. </li>
</ul>
<li>Screen style</li>
<li>First page when opening a patient record:</li>
<li>.... </li>
</ul>
<li>...... </li>
</ul>
<li>.....</li>
</ul>
<li>Management of user information:</li>
<ul>
<li>By the network manager:</li>
<ul>
<li>In begin the direction of the healthcare organization has a
global responsibility, particularly the responsibility to delegate
missions to well identified and accredited collaborators.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li>This is why the management of key information is restricted
to the network manager:</li>
<ul>
<li>Creation of new users,</li>
<li>Professional accreditaion,</li>
<li>Delegations of authorizations, which kind of information
may be read and/or modified. </li>
</ul>
</ul>
<li>By the users themselves:</li>
<ul>
<li>Most other information should be be maintained by the user
himself.</li>
<li>The user's preference may be modified at any time by the user
himself.</li>
</ul>
<li>Remark:&nbsp; anyhow, any changes in the user profile will be
traced. </li>
</ul>
</ul>





